• # Codewith Changelog

  ## [Unreleased]

  ### Added

  - Added /tmux --session <name> --window <name> handoff support so an active
    Codewith TUI can move into a specific existing tmux session and window,
    while
    preserving the existing automatic session creation behavior when no target
    is
    supplied.
